            <!-- About Me Section -->
            <div class="section hidden" id="about">
                <h2>About Me</h2>
                <div class="card">
                    <p>I’m Pravalika Kethadi, a passionate Salesforce Administrator and Developer with over 3 years of hands-on experience in the Salesforce ecosystem. I specialize in building intelligent, scalable solutions that streamline operations and elevate user experience.

My journey began in India, where I gained strong experience in both Salesforce administration and development. On the admin side, I’ve worked extensively with Flows, Approval Processes, Process Builder, and Workflow Rules to automate business logic. I’m well-versed in sharing and security features like role hierarchies, profiles, permission sets, OWDs, and sharing rules, as well as using Record Types, Web-to-Case, Email-to-Case, Case Assignment Rules, and Escalation Rules to drive service excellence.

My technical toolkit also includes Apex Classes, Triggers, Test Classes, and Lightning Web Components (LWC) for custom development. I've built and maintained solutions across Sales Cloud, Service Cloud, and Experience Cloud (Community Cloud) environments.

At the heart of it, I love solving complex CRM challenges, automating repetitive tasks, and creating Salesforce experiences that truly support business growth.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

